item.title: CVE-2019-5912|2024-08-04T20:09:23.739Z -- micco -- the%20installer%20of%20unarj32.dll
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in the installer of UNARJ32.DLL (UNARJ32.DLL for Win32 Ver 1.10.1.25 and earlier) allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
